{"tid":1646700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沙田一間幼稚園20名學童有上呼吸道感染　情況穩定","createTime":"2019-10-11T12:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T12:05:11.000Z","uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"17b35891d8ed2609ac0889fbc1df8ee1d831053f","tid":1646700,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485616-20191011.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485616-20191011.htm&d=6p%2BW5B2gHvlBGPj8iPYwcm6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=3d5b1784\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1485616-20191011.htm&h=ea1b8ca0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1485616-20191011.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田耀榮中英文幼稚園爆發上呼吸道感染，涉及12名男童及8名女童，年齡介乎2至5歲，所有人情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心表示，涉事學童自上月20日起出現發燒、咳嗽、流鼻水和喉嚨痛等上呼吸道感染病徵，其中12人已求醫，當中1人需入院，經治療後已出院。<br />\n<br />\n中心人員已視察該幼稚園，並提供有關預防建議，學校正接受醫學監察。"},{"pid":"3ada47e8cc5e41b78d3eb851d8829dbfaa60b7c8","tid":1646700,"uid":36901,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"為己為人<br />\n請戴口罩"},{"pid":"ae8808be732936ec8244977ba416742f9c56941e","tid":1646700,"uid":44298,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:04:24.000Z","msg":"咁而家戴唔戴得口罩啊"},{"pid":"4391a243c2e70bca9e488f7497500b0b35b980e2","tid":1646700,"uid":8441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:04:28.000Z","msg":"唔戴口罩丫拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cd3715c9318625f40b31a1ad35e209ba238436c","tid":1646700,"uid":68598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T12:05:11.000Z","msg":"繼續唔好戴 爆多d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no